    "whatsnew.v450.housetypes.b1": "User-creatable per project, with 48 country presets out of the box.",
    "whatsnew.v450.housetypes.b2": "Coverage from DE, US, UK and RU to TR, FR, ES, IT, PL, JP, CN and SA.",
    "whatsnew.v450.housetypes.b3": "Add custom types inline while creating a plot — no settings detour.",
    "whatsnew.v450.installer.title": "Installer reliability",
